title: Nino Schurter: Master of the Trail
description:
World Cross-Country MTB Champ Nino Schurter roams the legendary trails of Southern Utah's Gooseberry Mesa and Guacamole aboard his Scott Genius LT. Schurter is much more than your typical World Cup XC racer; his love for speed and style while discovering and exploring challenging lines help him Master the Trail.

Song: Fist Full of Steel
Artist: Rage Against The Machine
Writer: Tim Commerford

asset.author: Oakley
